@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title State Machine Diagram: Bid Lifecycle

[*] --> Submitted : Submit Bid
Submitted --> Pending : Awaiting Tourist Selection
Pending --> Accepted : Selected by Tourist
Accepted --> Confirmed : Driver Accepts
Confirmed --> Declined : Driver Declines
Accepted --> Declined : Driver Declines
Pending --> Rejected : Not Selected / Itinerary Cancelled
Confirmed --> Completed : Trip Completes
Completed --> [*]
Declined --> [*]
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml
